flowchart TD
  A[Trigger: Detection of engineering changes, volume/schedule changes, or contract disputes.]
  A --> N1[Stream: DDM/Crawlers - Detect engineering changes]
  N1 --> N2[Cortex: Cortex Auto Forecast - Assess commercial impact]
  N2 --> N3{PB: CWB Lifecycle - Negotiate price adjustments}
  N3 -->|Primary| N4[PB: Process Builder - Draft contract amendments]
  N4 --> N5[PB: Remote Functions - Execute contract amendments]
  N5 --> N6[PB: Remote Functions - Process retroactive adjustments]
  N6 --> Z1[Outcome: Reduced gross COGS, improved on-time delivery, enhanced margin protection.]
  N3 -->|No agreement reached during negotiation| B1[Escalate to human review]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Manual intervention required for further negotiation.]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|Contract dispute identified| B2[Initiate dispute resolution process]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Retroactive adjustments processed after resolution.]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|Volume/schedule change detected| B3[Adjust production plans and renegotiate contracts]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Updated contracts and production schedules.]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]